# Force LF in the working tree, overriding core.autocrlf=true.
#
# With autocrlf on, git rewrites these files to CRLF on checkout. That breaks exact-match editing
# (Edit fails against text that Read displays verbatim), makes grep report sources as binary, and
# fails `npm run check:bytes`. See CLAUDE.md.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary — never touch line endings.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.db binary
*.sqlite binary
